Syntax-Collector
================

Created:      2012-02-15
Home page:    <https://metacpan.org/release/Syntax-Collector>
Bug tracker:  <http://rt.cpan.org/Dist/Display.html?Queue=Syntax-Collector>
Maintainer:   Toby Inkster (TOBYINK) <tobyink@cpan.org>

0.005	2013-11-20

 [ BACK COMPAT ]
 - Almost complete rewrite, subclassing Exporter::Tiny.
 - The IMPORT method no longer gets passed @_ from import, and is now
   undocumented.

 [ Packaging ]
 - Drop Sub::Name dependency.
 - Drop Test::Exception dependency.
 - Drop Test::Warn dependency.
 - Drop syntax.pm dependency.

0.004	2012-09-07

 [ Documentation ]
 - Clean up documentation.

 [ Packaging ]
 - Drop PerlX::Maybe dependency.

0.003	2012-05-11

 [ Packaging ]
 - Drop Sub::Uplevel dependency.

 [ Other ]
 - Added: Support an 'into' parameter.
 - Borrow caller-fooling technique from Import::Into, so we no longer need
   uplevel.
 - IMPORT methods now get passed @_ from import.

0.002	2012-02-16

 - Cope better with modules that inherit their import routine.
 - Make Sub::Uplevel more aggressive.

0.001	2012-02-16	Initial release
